commitResults.messageTitle: Renamed chatbot from Duke to Dasani with basic greeting and exit functionality
Implement echo functionality for user commands and handle exit with 'bye'
Enhanced Dasani chatbot with emoji-based personality and UI improvements
Add text storage feature and list stored text upon user request
Add Task class to represent tasks in the task list
Refactor Dasani class to integrate Task class for task management
commitResults.messageBody:
Replaced primitive task tracking with Task objects
Improved task list printing with status indicators ([X] / [ ]])
Added commands for marking and unmarking tasks

commitResults.messageTitle: Enhance task validation for marking/unmarking and checking of task existence
Refactor task management for better readability and validation
commitResults.messageBody:
- Introduced TaskManager class to encapsulate task-related logic
- Improved input validation and error handling for task commands

commitResults.messageTitle: Add support for ToDos, Deadlines, and Events using inheritance
commitResults.messageBody:
- Implemented `Todo`, `Deadline`, and `Event` classes inheriting from `Task`
- Updated `TaskManager` to handle different task types dynamically
- Added validation for empty task lists

commitResults.messageTitle: Add automated Text UI testing using I/O redirection
